column5: The best way to beat the gas price is go up and don't come back.
if your not dragging a boat it might not be to bad and going in a honda or toyota
Could be cheaper to fly in.Say hi to my buddy Dave.he guides there.
Get your trips in early fella's

Probably so but when you think of the group going, it’s probably another $50-$75 per person. I’d skip on live bait and eat fish for a week vs some gourmet crap meal you have to buy and back to even. It sucks but gas prices wouldn’t make me cancel a trip.
I wonder what prices will be at the Dock ?
I got a cheap 7 day flyin in sept,it can go to 7$ for all I care,gonna slay'em.
I wonder what Aviation fuel will be a gallon or Liter ?
$1.97 a Liter in FF (7.48) a gal. As of today
A person can off set that,instead of eating 2 eggs have 1,instead of having 6 pieces of bacon have 3,there's ways to make up for high gas price.
The only way to Beat the HIGH GAS PRICES IS.............dont go 🤣
